<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Transfer OTP Verification</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #121212;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 500px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #1e1e1e;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }
        .logo {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .logo img {
            width: 150px; /* Adjust the size of your logo */
        }
        .title {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .otp-box {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #4caf50;
            background: #292929;
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #bbb;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #4caf50;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        p {
            color: white !important;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="logo">
            <img style="width:70px;height:70px" src="<%= marketplaceUrl%>/assets/_images/flutterwave-logo.png" alt="Company Logo">
        </div>

        <p>Dear <strong><%= data.user.firstname %> <%= data.user.lastname %></strong>,</p>
        <p>You requested to transfer <span class="highlight"><%= data.amount %></span> to <%= data.walletToCredit %></p>
        <p>To complete your transfer, please use the OTP code below:</p>

        <div class="otp-box"><%= otp %></div>

        <p>This OTP is valid for the next <strong>2 minutes</strong>. Do not share this code with anyone.</p>

        <p>If you did not request this transfer, please contact our customer support immediately.</p>

        <p><strong>Phone:</strong> +44-273874848838</p>
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:support@crygoca.com">support@crygoca.com</a></p>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Thank you for choosing <strong>Crygoca</strong>.</p>
            <p>The Crygoca Team</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
